  ./COVERAGE.md:961:| `org.apache.pekko:pekko-protobuf-v3_3` | [1.0.1<br>- 2.0.0-M3](metadata/org.apache.pekko/pekko-protobuf-v3_3/index.json) | <details><summary>Show</summary> Apache Pekko Protobuf V3 packages the Google Protocol Buffers Java runtime shaded under org.apache.pekko.protobufv3.internal for use by Pekko modules. The relocation lets Pekko depend on protobuf serialization internals without exposing or conflicting with applications' own com.google.protobuf dependencies.</details> | [100.0% (161/161 calls)](stats/org.apache.pekko/pekko-protobuf-v3_3/) |
