ex.json:9:    \"description\" : \"Apache Pekko Parsing is a Scala-specific internal support module for Pekko HTTP that provides compile-time logging guards and cross-Scala-version compatibility annotations used by the HTTP parsing implementation. It is published as a JVM JAR for each Scala binary version, including Scala 3, so downstream Pekko HTTP modules can share those internal helpers without duplicating them.\",\n./metadata/org.apache.pekko/pekko-parsing_2.13/index.json:9:    \"description\" : \"Apache Pekko Parsing is a Scala-specific internal support module for Pekko HTTP that provides compile-time logging guards and cross-Scala-version compatibility annotations used by the HTTP parsing implementation. It is published as a JVM JAR for each Scala binary version, including Scala 2.13, so downstream Pekko HTTP modules can share those internal helpers without duplicating them.\",\n./metadata/org.apache.pekko/pekko-actor_2.13/1.1.5/reachability-metadata.json:303:      \"type\" : \"org.apache.pekko.dispatch.PekkoJdk9ForkJoinPool\",\n./metadata/org.apache.pekko/pekko-actor_2.13/index.json:5:    \"source-code-url\" : \"https://repo.maven.apache.org/maven2/org/apache/pekko/pekko-actor_2.13/$version$/pekko-actor_2.13-$version$-sources.jar\",\n./metadata/org.apache.pekko/pekko-actor_2.13/index.json:8:    \"documentation-url\" : \"https://repo.maven.apache.org/maven2/org/apache/pekko/pekko-actor_2.13/$version$/pekko-actor_2.13-$version$-javadoc.jar\",\n./metadata/org.apache.pekko/pekko-actor_2.13/index.json:9:    \"description\" : \"Apache Pekko Actor provides the core actor-system runtime for building concurrent, distributed, resilient message-driven JVM applications in Java and Scala. It includes the classic actor APIs, dispatching, supervision, routing, scheduling, event streams, configuration integration, and foundational utilities used by other Pekko modules.\",\n./metadata/org.apache.pekko/pekko-protobuf-v3_2.13/index.json:8:    \"description\" : \"Apache Pekko Protobuf V3 packages a shaded Google Protocol Buffers v3 Java runtime under the org.apache.pekko.protobufv3.internal namespace for Pekko modules. It lets Pekko use protobuf serialization without exposing or conflicting with application-level protobuf dependencies.\",\n./metadata/org.apache.pekko/pekko-protobuf-v3_2.13/index.json:15:      \"2.0.0-M1\"\n./metadata/org.apache.pekko/pekko-protobuf-v3_2.13/index.json:28:    \"description\" : \"Apache Pekko Protobuf V3 packages a shaded Google Protocol Buffers v3 Java runtime under the org.apache.pekko.protobufv3.internal namespace for Pekko modules. It lets Pekko use protobuf serialization without exposing or conflicting with application-level protobuf dependencies.\",\n./metadata/org.apache.pekko/pekko-protobuf-v3_2.13/index.json:47:    \"description\" : \"Apache Pekko Protobuf V3 packages the Google Protocol Buffers Java runtime shaded under org.apache.pekko.protobufv3.internal for use by Pekko modules. The relocation lets Pekko depend on protobuf serialization internals without exposing or conflicting with applications' own com.google.protobuf dependencies.\",\n./metadata/org.apache.pekko/pekko-protobuf-v3_2.13/index.json:65:    \"description\" : \"Apache Pekko Protobuf V3 packages the Google Protocol Buffers Java runtime shaded under org.apache.pekko.protobufv3.internal for use by Pekko modules. The relocation lets Pekko depend on protobuf serialization internals without exposing or conflicting with applications' own com.google.protobuf dependencies.\",\n./metadata/org.apache.pekko/pekko-protobuf-v3_3/index.json:9:    \"description\" : \"Apache Pekko Protobuf V3 packages the Google Protocol Buffers Java runtime shaded under org.apache.pekko.protobufv3.internal for use by Pekko modules. The relocation lets Pekko depend on protobuf serialization internals without exposing or conflicting with applications' own com.google.protobuf dependencies.\",\n./metadata/org.apache.pekko/pekko-protobuf-v3_3/index.json:28:    \"description\" : \"Apache Pekko Protobuf V3 packages the Google Protocol Buffers Java runtime shaded under org.apache.pekko.protobufv3.internal for use by Pekko modules. The relocation lets Pekko depend on protobuf serialization internals without exposing or conflicting with applications' own com.google.protobuf dependencies.\",\n./metadata/org.apache.pekko/pekko-protobuf-v3_3/index.json:40:      \"2.0.0-M1\"\n./metadata/org.apache.pekko/pekko-protobuf-v3_3/index.json:52:    \"description\" : \"Apache Pekko Protobuf V3 packages the Google Protocol Buffers Java runtime shaded under org.apache.pekko.protobufv3.internal for use by Pekko modules. The relocation lets Pekko depend on protobuf serialization internals without exposing or conflicting with applications' own com.google.protobuf dependencies.\",\n./tests/src/org.apache.directory.server/apacheds-i18n/2.0.0-M15/gradle.properties:4:library.coordinates = org.apache.directory.server:apacheds-i18n:2.0.0-M15\n./tests/src/org.apache.directory.server/apacheds-i18n/2.0.0-M15/gradle.properties:5:library.version = 2.0.0-M15\n./tests/src/org.apache.directory.server/apacheds-i18n/2.0.0-M15/gradle.properties:6:metadata.dir = org.apache.directory.server/apacheds-i18n/2.0.0-M15/\n./tests/src/org.apache.directory.server/apacheds-kerberos-codec/2.0.0-M15/gradle.properties:4:library.coordinates = org.apache.directory.server:apacheds-kerberos-codec:2.0.0-M15\n./tests/src/org.apache.directory.server/apacheds-kerberos-codec/2.0.0-M15/gradle.properties:5:library.version = 2.0.0-M15\n./tests/src/org.apache.directory.server/apacheds-kerberos-codec/2.0.0-M15/gradle.properties:6:metadata.dir = org.apache.directory.server/apacheds-kerberos-codec/2.0.0-M15/\n./tests/src/com.softwaremill.sttp.shared/pekko_3/1.5.1/src/test/scala/com_softwaremill_sttp_shared/pekko_3/Pekko_3Test.scala:25:import sttp.capabilities.pekko.PekkoStreams\n./tests/src/com.softwaremill.sttp.shared/pekko_3/1.5.1/src/test/scala/com_softwaremill_sttp_shared/pekko_3/Pekko_3Test.scal